main event: A woman in Natrona Heights, Pennsylvania saw a strange, circular object in the sky in 1966.
interesting points: The object was stationary and seemed to hover in the sky at first.
The object then suddenly shot off at a high rate of speed, disappearing from sight within seconds.
The witness reported the sighting to the local police, but they did not seem very interested.
The witness stated she had never seen anything like this before and considers herself a rational person.
The object was described as circular in shape and having a dull glow.
